---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import GitHubIcon from '../icons/github.svg?raw';
import PayPalIcon from '../icons/paypal.svg?raw';
import KoFiIcon from '../icons/kofi.svg?raw';
import BmcIcon from '../icons/bmc.svg?raw';
import RazorPayIcon from '../icons/razorpay.svg?raw';
import TriangleInfoIcon from '../icons/triangle-info.svg?raw';
import { DODO_DONATION_PAYMENT_LINK } from 'astro:env/client';
---

<Layout title="Support Sim8085" showActions={false} fullwidth={false} fullHeight={false}>
    <main class="privacy-policy max-w-4xl mx-auto py-8 px-4">
        <h1 class="text-2xl mb-6 font-bold">‚ù§Ô∏è Support Sim8085</h1>
        <p class="mb-2 leading-relaxed">
            If this project has been helpful to you, I'm truly grateful for the opportunity to make a difference.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-2 leading-relaxed">
            Please consider buying a virtual coffee or making a small donation to help me continue working on projects like this.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">
            Every contribution matters. üôè
        </p>
        <!-- Payment Options Section -->
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 items-center bg-main-background px-4 pt-8 pb-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">

            <!-- üî∂ Razorpay ‚Äî Primary CTA -->
            <div class="w-full max-w-md text-center" title="Recommended for Indian users">
                <a
                    href={`${DODO_DONATION_PAYMENT_LINK}?quantity=1&redirect_url=https://www.sim8085.com%2Fdonation-thank-you%2F"`}
                    class="payment-link rounded bg-terminal px-4 py-2 text-white hover:bg-terminal-700 transition"
                >
                    Donate Now
                </a>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-secondary-foreground italic">
                Supports UPI, Cards, NetBanking and international payments.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- üí≥ Secondary Options -->
            <div class="w-full max-w-4xl grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 justify-items-center pt-4 border-t border-dashed border-secondary-border">
                
                <div title="For international supporters">
                <a target="_blank" href="https://ko-fi.com/O4O8170QHN" class="payment-link text-xl flex gap-1 items-center text-active-foreground hover:text-blue-foreground">
                    <Fragment set:html={KoFiIcon} />
                    <span>Ko-Fi</span>
                </a>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-secondary-foreground">PayPal or Card</p>
                </div>

                <div title="Alternative for PayPal users">
                <form action="https://www.paypal.com/ncp/payment/9W3T973GRR7LN" method="post" target="_top">
                    <button class="text-xl flex gap-1 items-center text-active-foreground hover:text-blue-foreground cursor-pointer" type="submit">
                    <Fragment set:html={PayPalIcon} />
                    <span>PayPal</span>
                    </button>
                </form>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-secondary-foreground">Great for international supporters</p>
                </div>

                <div title="May not work for accounts outside India.">
                <a target="_blank" href="https://www.buymeacoffee.com/debjit.biswas" class="payment-link text-xl flex gap-1 items-center text-active-foreground hover:text-blue-foreground">
                    <Fragment set:html={BmcIcon} />
                    <span>Buy Me a Coffee</span>
                </a>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-secondary-foreground">Card payments only</p>
                </div>

                <div title="Via GitHub Sponsors">
                <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/sponsors/debjitbis08?o=esb" class="payment-link text-xl flex gap-1 items-end text-active-foreground hover:text-blue-foreground">
                    <Fragment set:html={GitHubIcon} />
                    <span>GitHub</span>
                </a>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-secondary-foreground">Best for recurring support</p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex mt-8 md:gap-16 items-start flex-wrap justify-stretch">
        </div>
    <div class="mt-6">
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Sim8085 is designed and maintained currently just by <a href="https://www.debjitbiswas.com">me</a>. Sometime ago I decided to leave my
            day job to focus full-time on projects like this. This decision allows me to continuously improve and add new features to the project, but it also means that I depend on donations for my livelihood.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
My goal is to create <a href="https://github.com/debjitbis08/logo">tools</a> and <a href="https://www.lambda-classes.com">courses</a> for students and developers to make their lives easier and help them learn.
        </p>


        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">üíé Sim8085 Plus</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            Sim8085 Plus is a one-time upgrade designed to support serious learners and power users. It unlocks useful features like:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
            <li>Saving unlimited files</li>
            <li>File versioning and history</li>
            <li>Future AI-powered tutorials and insights</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            There‚Äôs no subscription ‚Äî just a simple one-time payment. If you use Sim8085 regularly and want to support its future, Plus is the best way to do so.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        You can learn more or upgrade from the <a href="/upgrade/" class="underline underline-offset-4">Pricing page</a>.
        </p>
            
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">üìä Revenue So Far</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            I believe in being transparent about what Sim8085 earns. As of now:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 text-sm">
            <li><strong>Donations:</strong> $3.11</li>
            <li><strong>Plus Plan:</strong> $8</li>
            <li><strong>Ad Revenue:</strong> $0</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            These numbers are small, but I'm grateful for every bit of support. It helps me stay focused on improving the project without external funding.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            <span class="underline underline-offset-4">If you're unable to donate</span>, there are other ways to show your support:
        </p>

            <div class="">
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <h3 class="font-bold mb-4">üì£ Spread the Word</h3>
                    <p>
                        Share Sim8085 with your classmates, colleagues, or on social media to help more people discover and benefit from it.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold mb-4">‚≠ê Star the Project on GitHub</h3>
                    <p>
                        Starring the repository not only shows your appreciation but also helps the project gain visibility and encourages contributions from the community.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-4 mb-6">
                        <a class="github-button" href="https://github.com/debjitbis08/sim8085" data-color-scheme="no-preference: light; light: light; dark: dark;" data-icon="octicon-star" data-size="large" data-show-count="true" aria-label="Star debjitbis08/sim8085 on GitHub">Star</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold mb-4">üí° Provide Feedback</h3>
                    <p>
                        Have suggestions or ideas? Share your thoughts on our <a href="https://github.com/debjitbis08/sim8085/discussions/categories/ideas">discussion forums</a> on GitHub and shape future updates.
                        You may also ask questions about 8085 ALP on the <a href="https://github.com/debjitbis08/sim8085/discussions/categories/q-a">Q&A forum</a>. Other students or educators may be able to answer your questions.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-4 mb-6">
                        <a class="github-button" href="https://github.com/debjitbis08/sim8085/discussions" data-color-scheme="no-preference: light; light: light; dark: dark;" data-icon="octicon-comment-discussion" data-size="large" aria-label="Discuss debjitbis08/sim8085 on GitHub">Discuss</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold mb-4">üõ†Ô∏è Contribute to the Project</h3>
                    <p>
                        If you're familiar with coding or documentation, consider contributing to the Sim8085 project on GitHub. I need help with writing the documentation for all the instructions and directives.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-4 mb-6">
                        <a class="github-button" href="https://github.com/debjitbis08/sim8085/fork" data-color-scheme="no-preference: light; light: light; dark: dark;" data-icon="octicon-repo-forked" data-size="large" data-show-count="true" aria-label="Fork debjitbis08/sim8085 on GitHub">Fork</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>


        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Additionally, I plan to create detailed tutorials on 8085 assembly language programming to make learning more effective. These tutorials will be priced affordably to ensure they remain accessible to students.
        </p>

        <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Thank you for your support in keeping Sim8085 running and improving ‚Äî it's your involvement that helps this tool continue to grow!
        </p>
    </div>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
@reference "tailwindcss";

a:not(.payment-link) {
    @apply text-[rgb(var(--sm-blue-foreground))]
}
</style>

<script is:inline defer src="https://buttons.github.io/buttons.js"></script>
